tid":1246884,"uid":265471,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:00:59.000Z","msg":"七一再有百萬人上街，習大大就會認同林鄭真係做唔到野"},{"pid":"0f398d6893ee03988f4958d6b3ad2fb363d75f2c","tid":1246884,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:02:36.000Z","msg":"和打機一樣，當你見到路上充滿敵人，就知道走對路了。<br />\n<br />\n有人問聯署字眼為何這樣，為何不具體，為何行文如此。<br />\n聯署是政治把戲，不是講道理，不是交計劃書。單一、出眾、Wild card，甚至用當撈侵行文的方式，令訊息夠punching，模糊是令當撈侵可以出wild card，做什麼也行，總統做嘢唔洗你教。<br />\n<br />\n至於有人說「我不喜愛當撈侵，不簽。」就是不動動你的蠢腦，適當時候做適當事，現在不是叫你投他一票。<br />\n<br />\n然後有人說這就是港獨，這不是港獨，是借美國對中共威脅，協助鞏固香港的實然主權，維持香港特殊的地位，並推動雙普選，完全合法合憲。先鞏固實際的自主權，港不港獨是之後的事，你和港獨派往後慢慢討論，不關這事。<br />\n<br />\n即刻簽，立刻簽，好好睇睇，多少少人，當撈侵好說話一點。<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4rankuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=e88eb32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation</a><br />\n簽完記得去email 按確認！"},{"pid":"26752922bcb37546d4257d1e4740190bf6f4b12d","tid":1246884,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"李怡心水清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a08690ba9fc1aeb33b61233344da0122bfb9323","tid":1246884,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T06:10:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dcc6f38b39f97c2dff04df73af64c8afaaaf4461","tid":1246884,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":